                            <button class="quick-btn bg-white border border-[#EADDFF] text-[#1D1B1E] hover:bg-[#FFDADA] hover:text-[#3B0912] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium transition-all" data-sentence="我学汉语学了两年。">我学汉语学了两年。</button>
