                            <button class="quick-btn bg-white border border-[#EADDFF] text-[#1D1B1E] hover:bg-[#FFDADA] hover:text-[#3B0912] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium transition-all" data-sentence="他跑得比我快多了。">他跑得比我快多了。</button>
                            <button class="quick-btn bg-white border border-[#EADDFF] text-[#1D1B1E] hover:bg-[#FFDADA] hover:text-[#3B0912] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium transition-all" data-sentence="虽然汉语很难，但是我很感兴趣。">虽然汉语很难...</button>
                            <button class="quick-btn bg-white border border-[#EADDFF] text-[#1D1B1E] hover:bg-[#FFDADA] hover:text-[#3B0912] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium transition-all" data-sentence="除了看电影，我还喜欢听音乐。">除了看电影...</button>
